data.title: Omari Sankofa II
data.meta_description: Omari Sankofa II is a staff writer for The Athletic, covering the Memphis Grizzlies. He previously covered Robert Morris hoops, college football and general assignments at the Pittsburgh Post-Gazette. He was born and raised in Detroit and graduated from Michigan State University.
data.text: Led by the dynamic duo of Ja Morant and Jaren Jackson Jr.  with some help from Dillon Brooks and others  Memphis has emerged as perhaps the biggest surprise in the NBA. Grizzlies writer Omari Sankofa answered a bunch of questions on Wednesday afternoon.
